comment._content:
I think it is Sutherland Dock on Cockatoo Island.  See Don Shearman's 1914 photo - 

[http://www.flickr.com/photos/donshearman/1854975602/]

Not sure about the date ...

comment.author: 18901029@N00
comment._content: It's definitely Sutherland Dock. The barrel roofed building at the middle left of the dock appears to be the same as the one just visible in he 1914 photo but the three story building behind it is not present in the 1914 photo or any of the others from that period making me think that it is some time later than this.
